Usage: import_module_model [-help] -cell <string> [-idx_pair <string>]
                           -inputs <string> [-libs] [-link_only]
                           [-rc_corner <string>] [-tag <string>] -type <string>

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>          # <module name> (string, required)
-idx_pair <string>      # <idx pair list if the files are copied from idx db>
                        # (string, optional)
-inputs <string>        # <full directory of the library file to be imported>
                        # (string, required)
-libs                   # <specify whether the input file is a library file or
                        # not> (bool, optional)
-link_only              # <link_only or hard_copy> (bool, optional)
-rc_corner <string>     # <rc corner if the type is qrc_tech>
                        # (string, optional)
-tag <string>           # <Specifies tag of a saved file. This option is mutual
                        # exclusive with -libs (string, optional)
-type <string>          # <type of library file : lib lef qrc_tech qrc_conf>
                        # (string, required)